{"tid":922240,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)閃電俠第1 2 5季","createTime":"2018-11-30T08:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T16:53:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31106ef82cf44f4a121d81455adf582ef4e2daa1","tid":922240,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=fTZlYgnirmZfPJI9v7UNyMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cbc1c72b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=fTZlYgnirmZfPJI9v7UNyMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5dfe8ab2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=fTZlYgnirmZfPJI9v7UNyMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=30c5912f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://cw1.tw/CW/opinion/images/common/old/tumblr_nxo8jsB3kB1tbsjlbo1_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcw1.tw%2FCW%2Fopinion%2Fimages%2Fcommon%2Fold%2Ftumblr_nxo8jsB3kB1tbsjlbo1_1280.png&h=ae26bb90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/d487e69aa790f97434a820ba8250e2c8/tenor.gif?itemid=8760194\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fd487e69aa790f97434a820ba8250e2c8%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D8760194&h=c0f99509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.11歲時，貝瑞&middot;艾倫(葛蘭特&middot;格斯汀飾)的母親諾拉離奇死亡，在目睹了母親離奇被殺，父親亨利&middot;艾倫被錯誤指認為兇手，貝瑞被亨利好友喬&middot;威斯特警探（傑西&middot; L&middot; 馬丁飾）一家收留。由於貝瑞沉溺於自己悲慘的過去，所以長大之後變成了一個聰明但是不善交際的中城警察局CSI犯罪現場員，在成長過程中，他一直沒有放棄過對於母親真正死因的調查，沒人相信他對犯罪的描述:「一個帶著閃電的黃衣高速人那晚入侵他們家」，所以喜歡研究冷門案件、超自然現象以及尖端科學的進展以試圖解釋他母親的謀殺案<br />\n<br />\n2.第一季結束貝瑞雖然成功戰勝艾爾伯德&middot;斯旺（Reverse Flash），可是卻因為與逆閃電（Reverse Flash）決戰時引發奇點，導致平行世界之間的通道打開，而吸引到地球二號的大反派極速（Zoom）的到來。<br />\n第二季最後一集季終，閃電俠看到自己的爸爸死在極速（Zoom）的手裡非常的憤怒，於是痛恨要殺死極速（Zoom）。但是極速（Zoom）創造了自己的時間餘線，把另外一個自己給殺死了，導致閃電俠無法順利殺死極速（Zoom）並且逃跑，於是閃電俠貝瑞決定要制定一個計畫讓極速（Zoom）死掉&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n5.思考者事件結束後，Barry發現有其他極速者幫忙擊毀衛星。慶功宴的當下，出現一個自稱Barry的女兒Nora Allen的女孩說道，她犯了一個錯誤。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=fTZlYgnirmZfPJI9v7UNyMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2e108a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a> 可能會播3掛<br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=fTZlYgnirmZfPJI9v7UNyMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9829f09a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadda93ad08b98ae65d706bc645ba744f4a5ebd2","tid":922240,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif